<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- أَوْ غَرْسِ شَجَرٍ فِيهَا.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- وَمَنْ سَبَقَ إِلَى طَرِيقٍ وَاسِعٍ؛<span class="c5"> فَهُوَ أَحَقُّ بِالجُلُوسِ فِيهِ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> مَا بَقِيَ مَتَاعُهُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> مَا لَمْ يَضُرَّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَيَجُوزُ جَعْلُ شَيْءٍ مَعْلُومٍ، لِمَنْ يَعْمَلُ عَمَلاً وَلَوْ مَجْهُولاً؛ كَرَدِّ عَبْدٍ، وَلُقَطَةٍ، وَبِنَاءِ حَائِطٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَمَنْ فَعَلَهُ بَعْدَ عِلْمِهِ:</span> اسْتَحَقَّهُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلِكُلٍّ فَسْخُهَا:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَمِنْ عَامِلٍ:</span> لَا شَيْءَ لَهُ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمِنْ جَاعِلٍ:</span> لِعَامِلٍ أُجْرَةُ عَمَلِهِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَإِنْ عَمِلَ غَيْرُ مُعَدٍّ لِأَخْذِ أُجْرَةٍ لِغَيْرِهِ عَمَلاً بِلَا جُعْلٍ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ مُعَدٌّ بِلَا إِذْنٍ:</span> فَلَا شَيْءَ لَهُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>-<span class="c5"> إِلَّا:</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> فِي تَحْصِيلِ مَتَاعٍ مِنْ بَحْرٍ أَوْ فَلَاةٍ: فَلَهُ أَجْرُ مِثْلِهِ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَفِي رَقِيقٍ: دِينَارٌ، أَوِ اثْنَا عَشَرَ دِرْهَماً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>